
::SAGA DOCUMENTATION FILE::

:ADAPTOR NAME:

  Default Advert Adaptor
  
:AUTHORS:

  Copyright (c) 2006-2009 Hartmut Kaiser (hkaiser@cct.lsu.edu)
 
:LICENSE:

  Distributed under the Boost Software License, Version 1.0.
  
:ADAPTOR LIBRARY NAME:
  
  libsaga_adaptor_default_advert.so (dylib)

:IMPLEMENTS PACKAGE:
 
  - saga_package_advert_service
  - saga_package_namespace

:DESCRIPTION:

  The adaptor allows access to database systems.  Currently supports SQLite (V3), and Postgresql V8.x upwards.

:URL SCHEMES:

  - advert://

:REQUIRES:

  An installation of PostgreSQL or SQLite

:CONFIGURE OPTIONS:

  | 
  | --with-postgresql-location=<dir>  use postgresql at <dir> (default=auto)    |\\
  | --with-sqlite3-location=<dir>     use sqlite3 at <dir> (default=auto)       |\\
  |                                                                             |\\
  |  SQLITE3_LOCATION             Location of SQLite installation directory     |
  |  POSTGRESQL_LOCATION          Location of postgreSQL installation directory |

:INI OPTIONS:

  none

:KNOWN ISSUES:

  See https://macpro01.cct.lsu.edu/trac/saga/query?status=assigned&status=new&component=Default+Advert+Adaptor&order=priority&col=id&col=summary&col=type&col=status&col=priority&col=milestone
